# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/).

`CHANGELOG.md` is the human-readable, project-level summary of notable changes.

`.changeset/` stores release-oriented change files for versioning and publish workflows. It complements this file rather than replacing it.

Practical rule:

- Add a changeset when a change should affect package versions or release notes.
- Update this file when you want a durable project-level summary for humans to scan.

